{"tid":362084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粵港澳大灣區　唐英年：10,000萬人生活自由往來　是一億人市場　哈哈哈","createTime":"2017-08-16T15:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T17:30:53.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03919fcde11c5990a8c662a335936ad22f13a1c7","tid":362084,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news_topic/nt_content.asp?sid=1805&amp;nt=np\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews_topic%2Fnt_content.asp%3Fsid%3D1805%26nt%3Dnp&d=PzCHRg2c2PS3tGfn3tPDNAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1152c891\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews_topic%2Fnt_content.asp%3Fsid%3D1805%26nt%3Dnp&h=488fe8d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news_topic/nt_content.asp?sid=1805&amp;nt=np</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/nt/images/993/1_2009072010420909376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnt%2Fimages%2F993%2F1_2009072010420909376.jpg&h=75e877cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唐英年接受本報專訪時，就描繪了一幅粵港融合的遠景。他認為，香港的出路，在於一國兩制《基本法》框架下的融合發展觀。朝着粵港融合的目標前進，香港的巿場規模可以由現在七百萬人口擴展至一億人口；香港人可以選擇一個更便宜更優質的生活環境，而在「一加一大於二」的優勢互補下，珠三角可以成為全國最具經濟活力的區域。<br />\n<br />\n　　剛剛走訪完珠三角九巿的唐英年，接受本報訪問，解釋今次走訪九巿的背景。他指出，國務院發表的《珠江三角洲地區改革發展規劃綱要》，是將粵港合作提升到國家層次，成為國家的戰略安排。他相信，連同港澳兩地，珠三角區有潛質可以成為全國最具經濟活力的經濟區，「單是廣東省已有九千萬人口，再加上港澳兩地，即共有接近一億人，是相當具規模的經濟容量，可以說是一個接近中型國家的經濟容量&hellip;&hellip;連同香港的生產總值比長三角還要高，我覺得我們是有潛質做全國最具經濟活力的一個區。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_140528/20140528_e5d20716ef895239c59fjCvMkkzDGN6I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_140528%2F20140528_e5d20716ef895239c59fjCvMkkzDGN6I.jpg&h=293e630f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12f63c3eebf0efb2ea11ab0d66a1944a6bc3cf34","tid":362084,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe31a4e77bc61749ad50f82a1ec340c87f173cc2","tid":362084,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:57:11.000Z","msg":"其實都啱嫁，以後話唔定港島變邊疆，新界人去深圳返工。"},{"pid":"53f5d2a60abd840f155b7f342266b4aee13be0f6","tid":362084,"uid":20256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"粵港澳國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a99574023fd65abfc70ca637ccc26d852ef845","tid":362084,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:05:35.000Z","msg":"啲相個感覺係諷刺緊篇新聞 咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f92a1fd0e0066c487061cc5849af0e40d9f46a","tid":362084,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"第二張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fe97ac8a18cb76f61543beed43e5b24b303311","tid":362084,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20140226/large/26la2p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140226%2Flarge%2F26la2p01.jpg&h=3b6a8f6c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}